title: Ep. - 321 - AARTI SEQUEIRA THE BACHELOR PREMIERE WITH LO VON RUMPF
description:
Kate reviews the season premiere of The Bachelor with celebrity stylist Lo Von Rumpf, host of the “The Lo Show” podcast.

 

Aarti Sequeira is an Indian cook and television personality, best known as the winner of the sixth season of Food Network's reality television show, The Next Food Network Star. In 2010, after her victory, her show Aarti Party premiered on the network. She is a featured chef and judge on various Food Network and Cooking Channel shows. She is now featured on Selena + Chef, which is on HBO Max. While in quarantine during the COVID-19 pandemic, singer Selena Gomez brushes up on her cooking skills with the help of master chefs.
